               <p>2d COUNT, stating them to be the property of George Aubrey and 
               <persName id="t18250217-41-victim305" type="victimName">
                  Isabella 
                  Bedford
               <interp inst="t18250217-41-victim305" type="surname" value="Bedford"></interp>
